			<h4><a id="comment_link_61485712" name="comment_link_61485712" href="//it.slashdot.org/comments.pl?sid=19098820&amp;cid=61485712" onclick="return D2.setFocusComment(61485712)" >Re:Not gonna happen</a>


		 	<span id="comment_score_61485712" class="score"> (<a href="#" onclick="getModalPrefs('modcommentlog', 'Moderation Comment Log', 61485712); return false"><span class=opt>Score:</span>5</a>, Informative)</span></h4>
		</div>
		<div class="details">
			<span class="by"><span class="byby">by </span><a href="//slashdot.org/~Geoffrey.landis">Geoffrey.landis</a>  <span class="uid"><a href="//slashdot.org/~Geoffrey.landis">( 926948 )</a></span></a></span><span class="writes" style="display:none"> writes:</span> 
			<span class="otherdetails" id="comment_otherdetails_61485712">		
		on Monday June 14, 2021 @09:44AM (<span class="ind"></span><a href="//it.slashdot.org/comments.pl?sid=19098820&amp;cid=61485712">#61485712</a>)
		<small><a href="http://www.geoffreylandis.com/" title="http://www.geoffreylandis.com/" class="user_homepage_display">Homepage</a> </small>
</span>
		</div>
